<item>
            <title>[SOLR-12068] Minor documentation correction in cdcr-config.html</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12068</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In sample source configuration for unidirectional approach in cdcr-config.html, the following are optional and not necessary at all, hence they should be emitted:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&amp;lt;updateRequestProcessorChain name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;cdcr-processor-chain&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;processor class=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;solr.CdcrUpdateProcessorFactory&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;processor class=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;solr.RunUpdateProcessorFactory&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/updateRequestProcessorChain&amp;gt;

&amp;lt;requestHandler name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/update&quot;&lt;/span&gt; class=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;solr.UpdateRequestHandler&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;lst name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;defaults&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;str name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;update.chain&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;cdcr-processor-chain&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;/lst&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/requestHandler&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

</description>
